item.title: One Fish, Two Fish
item.description:
On Friday night we took advantage of the aquarium’s last discount priced Friday night of the season and enjoyed some family fun.
We took 293 pictures during our 3 hours at the aquarium. From those we narrowed down 42 keepers. And from those, I have the difficult task of dwindling down some for the blog. The kids favorite part of the evening was the dolphin show.
